</table>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Sakoku" title="Sakoku">Sakoku</a></div>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:First_Japanese_treatise_on_Western_anatomy.jpg" class="image" title="Japan's first treatise on Western anatomy, published in 1774, an example of Rangaku."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/85/First_Japanese_treatise_on_Western_anatomy.jpg/180px-First_Japanese_treatise_on_Western_anatomy.jpg" width="180" height="113" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
