<td class="mbox-text" style=""><a href="/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons" title="Wikimedia Commons">Wikimedia Commons</a> has media related to: <i><b><a href="http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:History_of_Japan" class="extiw" title="commons:Category:History of Japan">Category:History of Japan</a></b></i></td>
